      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Matthew 24:29",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The same images used here with reference to the sun and moon are used also there: They occur not infrequently, ",
