        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Peter 3:7-10",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The shining of the sun is an emblem of prosperity; the withdrawing, the eclipse, or the setting of the sun is an emblem of calamity, and is often thus need in the Scriptures, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
