          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "verse-link",
            "text": "2 Samuel 7:23",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ". This will apply to any day in which God signally manifests himself, but particularly to a day when he shall come forth to punish people, as at the destruction of Jerusalem, or at the day of judgment. The meaning is, that those wonders would take place before that distinguished day should arrive when God would come forth in judgment. ",
            "children": []
